<h1>Draw</h1>
<p><a href='apps/draw/draw.html' target='_blank'>OPEN</a></p>

<h4>Introduction</h4>
<p>Web drawing program implemented in HTML/JS. It has functionality to draw with rotations and symmetry.</p>
<img src='images/draw_1.png' width='300' height='300'><img src='images/draw_2.png' width='300' height='300'>

<h4>Features</h4>
<ul>
  <li>Supports square canvas of any resolution</li>
  <li>Can draw in single line, rotations, and rotations with symmetry</li>
  <li>Configurable number of rotations</li>
  <li>Different brush types</li>
  <li>Undo/Redo function</li>
  <li>Can save image as PNG</li>
  <li>Implemented entirely in a single HTML file</li>
</ul>

